Notwithstanding any other provision of this Agreement, the license granted herein is conditional upon receipt of full payment of all outstanding invoices. Title to the Intellectual Property and the right to permanent use shall only transfer to the Client upon the successful settlement of all project fees. Until such time, this license is considered "Provisional" and may be revoked at the Developer’s discretion.
